sqlViews.name: ownership_updates
sqlViews.sqlQuery:
SELECT program.name as program_name, program.uid as program_uid, pi.uid as curr_enr_uid, po.Lastupdated as po_lastUpdated, 
po.created as po_created,  DATE(po.Lastupdated) as po_date, ou.uid as po_orgunit_uid,
 ou.name as po_ou_name,  ou2.uid as original_ou_uid, ou2.name as original_ou_name

from trackedentityprogramowner as po

LEFT JOIN program ON program.programid = po.programid
LEFT JOIN organisationunit AS ou ON ou.organisationunitid= po.Organisationunitid
LEFT JOIN programinstance as pi on pi.trackedentityinstanceid = po.Trackedentityinstanceid
LEFT JOIN trackedentityinstance as tei on tei.Trackedentityinstanceid = po.Trackedentityinstanceid
LEFT JOIN organisationunit AS ou2 ON ou2.organisationunitid= pi.organisationunitid

where po.Lastupdated != po.Created
sqlViews.description: fetches all updates to program ownership. Recommend filters for program uid and date in url.
